headline: Hasbro Women Innovators of Play Returns for Third Annual Virtual Event and Challenge
summary: PAWTUCKET, R.I., September 23, 2025--Hasbro, Inc. (NASDAQ: HAS), a leading games, IP, and toy company, today announced its Hasbro Women Innovators of Play 2025 lineup of events to celebrate and connect women toy and game innovators worldwide. The third annual program launches on October 9, 2025, building on the remarkable success of 2024.

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Turn Down
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.
